                                            href="/utilities/spacing.php#Margin-and-padding"> margin utilities</a>,
                                        developers may offset grid columns in two different ways. In contrast to
                                        <code>margins</code>, which are more suited for rapid layouts since the offset's
                                        width is <code>flexible</code>, grid classes are proportioned to match columns.
